reportJtagInst(25.10)                                    reportJtagInst(25.10)

Name
       reportJtagInst - Displays JTAG information specified by the specifyJtag
       command or creates an output file that contains the information

Syntax
       reportJtagInst

       [-outfile]

       Displays  JTAG information specified by the specifyJtag command or cre-
       ates an output file that contains the information.

Parameters
       -outfile
              Specifies the name of the file. If you do not specify this para-
              meter, the command prints the information to the screen  without
              saving it in a file.

Related Information
              * specifyJtag

              * Placing the Design chapter in the Innovus User Guide

                * Specifying  and  Placing  JTAG  and Other Cells Close to the
                  I/Os

